name: Order of the Glass Apes Anniversary

metadata.description:
A fresh face joins Order of the Glass Apes to mark the original collection’s 1 year Anniversary! 

Order of the Glass Apes Anniversary features a reimagined Bored Ape Yacht Club 8486, created in 2022 with permission from Snakezinc, BAYC ID: 8486.

Hand-drawn digital illustration by Brian Morris • 2400x2400 • PNG

Original collection: orderoftheglassapes.com
